# for arch installation:

choose locale en-Us
boot loader at /boot and use systemd one

setxkbmap -layout be




# for wifi install: 
https://packages.debian.org/buster/firmware-brcm80211

https://askubuntu.com/questions/1260846/wifi-not-working-on-lubuntu-20-04

install of busenlabs on z83s

1. install last busenlabs (with wired network)
2. sudo apt install firmware-brcm80211
3. cd /lib/firmware/brcm
sudo wget https://github.com/armbian/firmware/raw/master/brcm/brcmfmac43430a0-sdio.txt
sudo modprobe -r brcmfmac
sudo modprobe brcmfmac
